## Development

```bash
# Install all dependencies
uv sync

# Run all tests
make test-all

# Lint all packages
make lint-all

# Serve docs
make docs-serve
```

## Adding a new package

```bash
mkdir -p packages/my-package/src/my_package packages/my-package/tests
# Add pyproject.toml to the new package
# It will be auto-discovered by UV workspace
```

